{
  "number": 1673,
  "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/1673",
  "title": "InstantSearch props are not all updated when they change",
  "body": "**Current behavior**\r\n\r\n the only props that are updated if changed on the `InstantSearch` component are `searchState`, `onSearchStateChange` and `createUrl`.\r\n\r\nAll the others: `appId`, `apiKey`, `indexName` and `searchParameters` can't be changed once the InstantSearch is mounted. \r\n\r\nThis behavior is not natural as you expect changes in props to have repercussion on InstantSearch.\r\n\r\n**Expected Behavior**\r\n\r\nProps are updated accordingly in new ones are provided. ",
